quick tip, if you use VSCode + child themes, you can hide the duplicate "blank" files that you want to hide from the editor to avoid clogging things up. In settings add `files.exclude`
```  "files.exclude": {
    "src/templates/active-area-of-research": true,
    "src/templates/article": true,
    "src/templates/basic": true,
  },```
